With this menu entry REMOVES ALL OBFS4 BRIDGES. OBFS4 Bridges are necessary for TorBox to bypass Tor blocking in a country. To use this feature of TorBox, you need to have at least one OBFS4 bridge. After removing all OBFS4 bridges, you should add new OBFS4 bridges again.

IMPORTANT
WITH REMOVING ALL OBFS4 BRIDGES, TorBox will directly connect to the Tor network, which is the default. However, instead of removing OBFS4 bridges, we recommend simply to deactivate them.

Would you really like to REMOVE ALL OBFS4 BRIDGES?
